# =============================================================================
# SLG — environment variables
# =============================================================================
# Copy this file to `.env` (same folder, no extension change) and fill in
# real values. The .env file is git-ignored — never commit secrets.
#
# Vite only exposes variables that start with VITE_ to the client. Restart
# the dev server after changing any value (Vite reads .env once at startup).
# =============================================================================

# ─── Contact form (Formspree) ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Where the inquiry form sends submissions. Sign up at https://formspree.io
# with the destination email address (e.g. studiolagorgona@gmail.com), create
# a form, and paste the endpoint here.
#
# Format: https://formspree.io/f/<your-form-id>
VITE_FORMSPREE_ENDPOINT=https://formspree.io/f/your-form-id-here
